main event: Witnesses in Washington, DC observed 3 bright objects in the sky at around 9:05 PM that maneuvered and shot down in a vertical direction.
interesting points: USAF radar at Andrews AFB confirmed the sighting.
The sightings occurred during a period of increased UFO activity in the area.
The objects were probably reflecting lights of some kind, possibly meteorological balloons.
The objects maneuvered and shot down in a vertical direction.
The sighting lasted for about 10 minutes.
